<h2 id="editors-notes">Editor’s notes</h2>

<p>In this lesson I’ll teach you how to play “Imagine” by John Lennon on the acoustic guitar. I’ll show you the intro &amp; verse riff, explain the chords, demonstrate the strumming patterns, and teach you how to add some fun flourish to various chords in order to capture Lennon’s piano sound. I hope you enjoy!</p>

<p>Video timestamps:</p>

<ul>
  <li>0:00 Preview &amp; agenda</li>
  <li>1:50 Intro &amp; Verse riff</li>
  <li>10:01 Pre-chorus chords &amp; strumming</li>
  <li>14:27 Chorus chords &amp; strumming</li>
  <li>17:17 Farewell &amp; playthrough</li>
</ul>

